# CampusConnect

CampusConnect is a student collaboration platform that helps students discover projects, connect with teammates, showcase skills, and build their professional network.

## Features

- User Authentication
- Student Directory
- Project Creation
- Join Requests
- Notifications
- Portfolio Links
- Protected Routes
- Real-time Infrastructure with Socket.IO
- Fully Deployed

## Tech Stack

Frontend:
- Next.js
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT

Deployment:
- Vercel
- Render
- MongoDB Atlas
